before you can see things more clearly.

264
00:22:42,550 --> 00:22:44,300
The two of you may go back now.

265
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:01,800
Brother Xiao Yan, don't get confused.

266
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:05,140
