269
00:23:18,130 --> 00:23:22,410
Xun'er, immediately send a carrier pigeon to Father.

270
00:23:22,410 --> 00:23:26,960
Tell him that the Cloud Mist Sect and the Star Fall Pavilion
are watching the Xiao family attentively.

271
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:28,970
