Xiao family for so long. Isn't it tiring?

319
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:51,160
Go back and deliver a message
to the Cloud Mist Sect's Grand Old Master.

320
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:54,790
Although my son was sent to the desert

321
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:59,300
and he no longer has the surname,
"Xiao," he's still my kin.

322
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:05,600
Come find me if there's a situation.
There's no need to give up what is close and look far.

323
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:08,560
